                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogasification and direct combustion integrated biomass boiler with built-in in-boiler gasification chamber",
                    "内置炉内气化室的加氢气化直燃一体生物质锅炉"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a hydrogasification and direct combustion integrated biomass boiler with a built-in boiler gasification chamber, and aims to solve the problems that when hydrogen is added into the boiler, the hydrogen cannot penetrate through biomass raw materials with different thicknesses, so that the combustion of the hydrogen is insufficient, and the like. Comprising a shell and an energy saver arranged on one side of the shell, a fire grate is arranged in the shell, a feeding hopper is fixed to the front end of the shell and located above the fire grate, a combustion chamber is formed in the shell, a middle arch wall located above the fire grate is fixed to the interior of the combustion chamber, and the middle arch wall is located above the fire grate. The combustion chamber is divided into a front-end chamber and a rear-end chamber by the middle arch wall; through the arrangement of the middle arch wall, the oxyhydrogen machine, the energy saver and the like, the added middle arch wall has the effect of double-sided heat storage radiation, gasified and combusted fuel penetrates through the middle arch wall along with the fire grate to reach the rear-end cavity to be continuously combusted, rotary mixed combustion is formed in the combustion cavity, a combustion power field is strengthened, and the combustion efficiency is improved. The carbon content in the biomass raw material can be reduced to the minimum, and the combustible part is fully combusted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提出了内置炉内气化室的加氢气化直燃一体生物质锅炉，以解决向锅炉内部添加氢气时，氢气往往不能穿过不同厚度的生物质原料，导致氢气燃烧不充分等问题；包括壳体、置于壳体一侧的节能器，所述壳体内设置有炉排，所述壳体的前端固定有进料斗，所述进料斗位于炉排的上方，所述壳体内设置有燃烧腔室，所述燃烧腔室的内部固定有位于炉排上方的中拱墙，所述中拱墙将燃烧腔室分为前端腔室和后端腔室；通过中拱墙、氢氧机和节能器等设置，增加的中拱墙具有双面蓄热辐射的作用，气化燃烧后的燃料随炉排穿过中拱墙到后端腔室继续燃烧燃尽，在燃烧腔室内形成旋转混燃，强化燃烧动力场，可将生物质原料中的含碳量降至最低、可燃部分充分燃烧。"
                }
